high_descs: Turn left and take a step forward, then walk over to the white counter.
Pick up the black pen off of the counter.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a right and walk up to the black table.
Put the black pen in the leftmost mug on the table.
Pick up the mug with the pen in it off of the table.
Walk back over to the white counter.
Put the mug with the pen in it on the counter to the left of the laptop.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a pen in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left, step forward, then turn left and step forward again, turn right and go to the counter.
Pick up the pencil located to the left of the bowl.
Turn around, head straight, turn right, walk forward then turn left to face a table.
Place the pencil in the first cup to the right of the lamp.
Pick up the cup with the pencil inside.
Turn around and return to the counter where the pencil was picked up.
Place the cup with the pencil to the left of the laptop.
anns.task_desc: Store the pencil in a cup and place back on counter.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to the bathroom area on the right
Pick up the pen from the counter in the bathroom
Turn around, walk to the table in the room to the right
Place the pen inside the mug on the table
Pick up the mug and pen that are on the table
turn around carry the mug and pen from the table to the counter in the bathroom
Set the mug and pen on the counter in the bathroom
anns.task_desc: Move mug and pen from room to the bathroom
